result.name: Sushi Tokumi

reviews.text:
Japanese restaurant in Whampoa famous.for it's sushi. I had lunch here and ordered a tempura set. Their silver cod set is very good. 

Located in a side street with no views. The food was warm but quite toasty. Service was fairly swift. Pricing is on the upper moderate side.

Very nice place for Japanese food. We had a group of ten and were in a room with a more traditional Japanese sitting arrangement. Comfortable with our legs sunken down while we sat on traditional seats without legs.
The food is good and fresh and not very expensive.
Not the first time been there. Definitely not the last time I will go there.
What an amazing experience served by the nice staff. the delicous japanese food should be shared to all tourists here.

Visit was due to they are one of the branches of the group restaurant, atmosphere inside are comfortable, prices & foods are average at this branch.
If comparing to the branch at Hau Fook Street of Tsim Sha Tsui, there have a  sushi bar and a bigger floor area, similar but difference theme of decorations inside, would prefer the Tsim Sha Tsui branch.

result.name: Sushi Tokumi

reviews.text:
Japanese restaurant in Whampoa famous.for it's sushi. I had lunch here and ordered a tempura set. Their silver cod set is very good. 

Located in a side street with no views. The food was warm but quite toasty. Service was fairly swift. Pricing is on the upper moderate side.
越做越差，食物越來越細碟 ，價錢超貴，燒牛舌越來越薄，坐門口第一張枱簡直冇冷氣，仲要全程畀人眼超超睇住你食乜，冇晒私隱， 一定冇下次， 奉勸大家想食好嘅日本嘢花少少時間搭車出尖沙咀佐敦好過
座位很迫，不認識的人两桌並排無空隙
租金太貴，一定要翻枱多幾運才可！

同朋友過開黎紅磡, 朋友提意食壽司, 想起紅磡都有德美, 之前在尖沙咀都有食過唔錯。 紅磡分店位於地舖, 餐廳門口掛著一排紅燈籠, 離遠都見到呢間就係德美。

時間未到晚上七點, 門口已經有人等位中, 在門口位置攞飛仔, 等咗大約5分鐘就有位了。

🔸牛肉湯烏冬🔸⭐⭐⭐⭐
原本想叫牛肉鍋但無烏冬, 問過店員其實湯底都一樣, 最後揀咗牛肉湯烏冬。 烏冬係有少少煙韌同比較粗嗰款, 配甜甜既湯底, 好味。

🔸火灸左口魚邊壽司🔸⭐⭐⭐⭐
愛上了火灸後既左口魚邊, 火燒到油脂出哂黎, 咬落好有滿足感💕

🔸帆立貝壽司🔸⭐⭐⭐⭐
超大隻帆立貝, 厚厚既肉好鮮甜。

🔸三文魚腩壽司🔸⭐⭐⭐
有個小插曲, 壽司黎到發現唔似腩位, 問問店員, 查明後都即時幫我地換返。
油脂分佈平均, 如果再多啲油脂仲正。

🔸吞拿魚腩茸壽司🔸⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
超級份量多, 多到一口未必食得哂, 不過就算先食部分吞拿魚茸都好好味, 近來喜歡了它。

🔸海老天婦羅🔸⭐⭐⭐
正常size味道無乜驚喜, 會有一條秋葵, 連埋炸蝦頭, 蝦頭仲會有少少蝦膏添。

🔸炸蠔卷🔸⭐⭐⭐⭐
除咗包咗四件飯卷, 另外會一開二既炸蠔, 味道唔錯, 配青瓜絲同醬汁都好味。
